Package: consumer.pkg
Type: Package
Title: Cross-Package Trait Dispatch Consumer Example
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mossa Merhi", "Reimert", , "mossa@struchstrup.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Eleanor", "Andersson", role = "ctb")
    )
Description: Demonstrates miniextendr's cross-package trait dispatch capabilities.
    Provides generic functions that operate on the Counter trait interface. Works
    with Counter implementations from any package (like producer.pkg), proving
    ABI compatibility via type tag matching and vtable dispatch.
